2/04/30/world/bosnia-student-kills-teacher-and-himself.html|website=www.nytimes.com/|accessdate=23 July 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| September 26, 2002\n| [[Lanzhou]], [[China]]\n| Yang Zhengming, 40\n| 2 dead\n| 2 injured\n| Yang Zhengming, who worked as a mini-bus driver for Number 34 Middle School in Lanzhou, killed a teacher and wounded two others at the school with a hunting rifle, one of the wounded being his former girlfriend. Police finally shot him dead after negotiating with him for two hours while he was standing on the roof and threatened to commit suicide.<ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/en/doc/2002-09/27/content_138081.htm Two dead in school shooting in northwest China city] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021225503/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/en/doc/2002-09/27/content_138081.htm |date=2012-10-21 }}, ''[[China Daily]]'' (September 27, 2002)</ref><ref>[http://muzi.com/cc/english/10351,19931.shtml?m=4&q=1227401 Driver shoots teacher in China campus killing] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714141206/http://muzi.com/cc/english/10351%2C19931.shtml?m=4&q=1227401 |date=2011-07-14 }}, ''muzi.com'' (September 27, 2002)</ref>\n|-\n| October 7, 2002\n| [[Bowie, Maryland]], United States\n| [[John Allen Muhammad]], 41<br>[[Lee Boyd Malvo]], 17\n|\n| 1 injured\n| A victim of the [[Beltway sniper attacks]], 13-year-old Iran Brown was shot and wounded as he arrived at [[Benjamin Tasker Middle School]] in [[Bowie, Maryland]]. His aunt, a nurse who had just brought him to school, rushed him to a hospital emergency room. Despite serious injuries, including damage to several major organs, Brown survived the attack.\n|-\n| October 28, 2002\n| [[Salvador, Brazil]]\n| E. R., 17\n| 2 dead\n| \n| A 17-year-old student identified as E. R., armed with an .38 revolver, shot Vanessa Carvalho Batista in the head, killing her instantly, he then fired shots at Natasha Silva Ferreira, both of them 15-year-old, seriously injuring her, in the Colegio Sigma. She then died at the hospital. E. R. then stayed on the school campus until police arrived, and threatened to commit suicide, but was convinced to not do so by his 21-year-old brother. The shooter said he did not have good relations with the two girls, and said that they ridiculed him publicly.<ref>[https://noticias.uol.com.br/inter/reuters/2002/10/28/ult27u27985.jhtm Estudante mata duas colegas dentro de escola em Salvador], ''UOL Not\u00edcias'' (October 28, 2002)</ref><ref>[http://www1.folha.uol.com.br/fsp/cotidian/ff2910200203.htm Na BA, estudante mata 2 colegas na sala de aula], ''[[Folha de S.Paulo]]'' (October 29, 2002)</ref><ref>[http://www.correio24horas.com.br/noticia/nid/relembre-caso-de-adolescente-que-matou-colegas-em-escola-em-salvador/ Relembre caso de adolescente que matou colegas em escola em Salvador], ''Correio'' (April 7, 2011)</ref>\n|-\n| December 27, 2002\n| [[Otniel]], [[West Bank]]\n| Two members of the Islamic Jihad group\n| 6 dead\n| 9 injured\n| [[Yeshivat Otniel shooting]]. Two Palestinian gunmen, who were members of the Islamic Jihad group, killed four students at Yeshivat Otniel, a Hesder Yeshiva in the Jewish settlement of Otniel near Hebron in the West Bank. <ref>[title: Gunmen Kill 4 Inside Yeshiva In West Bank |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2002/12/28/world/gunmen-kill-4-inside-yeshiva-in-west-bank.html |date=December 28, 2002 |website= The New York Times |author= Dexter Filkins</ref>\n|-\n| January 26, 2003\n| [[Guangdong|Suixi county]], [[China]]\n| Chen Peiquan, 35\n| 4 dead\n| 3 injured\n| Chen Peiquan, an English teacher with a history of mental problems, stabbed six students and a teacher in a dormitory at Yang Gan Middle School, killing four of them. He was arrested after fleeing to the roof of the building.<ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/en/doc/2003-01/28/content_153227.htm Teacher stabs seven in China, three children and a teacher die], ''[[China Daily]]'' (January 28, 2006)</ref><ref>[http://www.news24.com/News24/World/0,6119,2-10_1312135,00.html Teacher goes berserk, kills 4]{{dead link|date=May 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}, ''[[News24]]'' (January 27, 2003)</ref>\n|-\n| January 27, 2003\n| [[Taiuva]], [[Brazil]]\n| Edmar Aparecido Freitas, 18\n| 1 dead\n| 8 injured\n| 18-year-old Edmar Freitas shot and wounded six students, a teacher and a janitor with a 38-caliber revolver at Escola Estadual Coronel Benedito Ortiz, his former school where he had been bullied for being overweight. He then committed suicide by shooting himself in the head.<ref>[http://www2.correioweb.com.br/cw/EDICAO_20030128/pri_ult_280103_215.htm Jovem invade escola, fere oito e se suicida], ''[[Correio Braziliense]]'' (January 28, 2003)</ref><ref>[http://www.educacional.com.br/reportagens/cultura_paz/default.asp Cultura de Paz \u2013 virando a mesa da violencia], ''educacional.com.br'' (February 14, 2003)</ref>\n|-\n| April 14, 2003\n| [[New Orleans, Louisiana]], United States\n| Steven Williams,<br>James Tate<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20080421113821/http://nola.live.advance.net/news/t-p/metro/index.ssf?%2Fbase%2Fnews-17%2F1158829217114200.xml&coll=1 4 plead guilty in killing at school \u2013 NOLA.com]. Nola.live.advance.net (2006-09-21). Retrieved on 2010-08-16.</ref>\n| 1 dead,\n| 4 injured\n| [[2003 John McDonogh High School shooting|John McDonogh High School shooting]]. 15-year-old Jonathan Williams, a student and football player, was fatally shot while sitting on the [[bleachers]] in the gymnasium of [[New Orleans Public Schools|John McDonogh Senior High School]], by two men armed with an [[AK-47]] [[assault rifle]] and a [[handgun]]. The two gunmen fired at least 18 rounds from their weapons, shattering Williams' face, and injuring three girls.\n|-\n| April 24, 2003\n| [[Red Lion, York County, Pennsylvania|Red Lion, Pennsylvania]], United States\n| James Sheets, 14\n| 2 dead\n|\n| [[Red Lion Area Junior High School shooting]]. 14-year-old student James Sheets, armed with [[.